STATE
v.
Jonathan E. BRUNSON 247P16-7 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019 Jonathan Eugene Brunson, for Brunson, Jonathan Eugene. Sherri Horner Lawrence, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 28th of May 2019 by Defendant for Petition for Rehearing of Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
